jetstream.description: A dark and powerful car built for speed, with an aggressive design and high-performance capabilities. Its sleek, aerodynamic form and cutting-edge technology make it a perfect choice for thrill-seekers.

turtle.name: Turtle
turtle.description: An avant-garde masterpiece, the Turtle redefines futuristic design with its sleek black finish and advanced aerodynamics. Equipped with cutting-edge technology and powerful performance, this epic rarity car is built to turn heads and command attention on the road.

duststorm.description: The Duststorm is a legendary powerhouse, engineered for extreme terrains with a monster truck build and a sleek silver finish. Its futuristic design combines brute strength with cutting-edge technology, making it an unstoppable force that dominates any landscape.
